|ShortSummary=Amanda poses as a wealthy jet-setter to attract the attention of a fast food chain owner who may be selling military secrets to the Soviets.
|LineColor=CDAD00 }}
|ShortSummary=Enemy agents targeting Lee accidentally kidnap Amanda in his place, demanding the release of their agent in return for Amanda.
|LineColor=CDAD00 }}
