|ShortSummary=Amanda agrees to help the Agency with a defecting Hungarian, who looks exactly like Francine.
|LineColor=CDAD00 }}
|ShortSummary=After failing repeatedly to catch a Bulgarian spy, Lee and Amanda are enlisted by "Blue Leader" to rule out a possible mole inside the Agency.
